parameters.Cult:
Factor giving the cultivar of the cabbage, two levels: c39
and c52.
parameters.HeadWt: Weight of the cabbage head, presumably in kg.
parameters.Date:
Factor specifying one of three planting dates: d16,
d20 or d21.
parameters.VitC: Ascorbic acid content, in undefined units.

title: Data from a cabbage field trial
